README

Steps to make Usher work on your tomcat
=======================================

1. Edit TOMCAT_LIB path in Makefile.

   e.g. TOMCAT_LIB='/usr/yourId/env/apache-tomcat/lib'

2. Run make.

3. Copy servlet-out/Usher.war into webapps directory of your Tomcat.

4. Check if following url work on the browser.

http://<yourTomCatLocation>:<port>/Usher/layout?data={"nodes":["n1","n2","n3","n4","n5","n6","n7"],"edges":[["n1","n2"],["n2","n3"],["n1","n4"],["n5","n4"],["n7","n4"],["n6","n3"]]}

Steps to make Usher work on your terminal
=========================================

Just run 'make test'.
